G-Shock was my first watch ever!

So when I heard the news that Ibe-san is coming down to town, I flew back from Melb to JKT so that I can tell him how much I adore everything he has created. I needed to show my gratitude to him. I wanted him to know that I actually spent my money on my first watch, and it was on his creation. He said “very nice, thank you very much!”. Later, he told me not to give up, and he reiterated these words on a t-shirt and this polaroid of mine. And I thought to myself “I will. I will Ibe-san”. I reckon manifestation is real huh🫠

Shoutout @hypebeastid @casiostore_id @gshockindo for the chance!

Happy birthday, Kid💌

Got a couple things to say. These aren’t wishes, these are words for you to keep.

Firstly, you are on your own now. Don’t stop exploring, make mistakes, be unapologetically yourself - they will dislike you nonetheless, don’t bat an eye. You will get hurt. You will be lied to. Trust nobody. You will also hurt people. Always apologise sincerely. Keep your circle small. Love those around you. Appreciate them with all your will. Show them you love them - don’t hold back affection. You don’t need to explain anything - those who love you won’t care, and those who don’t won’t believe you. Stay the way you are. You will have a massive influence - use it wisely. Don’t let nothing change you. Not money, not fame, not power. Always be the light for others, the way your parents named you after.
